Sentencas: The direct carbon fuel cells with solid oxide electrolyte (DC-SOFC) and anodes deposited by inject printing (EM/DCIJP) were studied.
Titulo: Feasibility of direct carbon solid oxide fuels cell (DC-SOFC) fabrication by inkjet printing technology

Sentencas: The cells were fed with carbon fuel obtained by the direct RF plasma splitting of methane.
Titulo: Feasibility of direct carbon solid oxide fuels cell (DC-SOFC) fabrication by inkjet printing technology

Sentencas: Since the (EM/DCIJP)M/DCIJP technology allows easy modification of electrode material, the effect of Cu addition to the Ni-YSZ anode was investigated.
Titulo: Feasibility of direct carbon solid oxide fuels cell (DC-SOFC) fabrication by inkjet printing technology

Sentencas: The significant improvement of the cell performance with the new anode was observed.
